For the purposes of this Policy, China Data Protection Law shall mean the Cybersecurity Law of the People's Republic of China (“PRC”), the PRC Data Security Law, the PRC Personal Information Protection Law, and all related, then current data protection provisions under the PRC Civil Code, other data protection related laws, regulations, administrative rules, administrative measures and national guidelines effective in China Mainland (together as “China Data Protection Law”).
