Identifiers and Information categories listed in the California Customer Records statute (Cal. Civ. Code § 1798.80(e)). These include names, telephone number, postal address, online identifier Internet Protocol address.
Commercial information such as products or services purchased, obtained, or considered, or other purchasing or consuming histories or tendencies.
Internet or other electronic network activity information, including, but not limited to, browsing history, search history, and information regarding a consumer’s interaction with the Service.
